Had a really amazing trip with my road dawg (who saved my ass and made the trip so smooth) @snelgrove  starting in Helsingor and Copenhagen, Denmark to celebrate @henning_royaltattoo & @royaltattoodk 40th shop anniversary. Then off to Barcelona where I got to eat lots of paella and drink tiny beers. Saw @chicapanteratattoo along with some amazing Gaudi, Flamenco dancing and new friends. Then off to Utrecht, Netherlands to see my family away from home @thevillagecoffee crew @feelslikeendtimes @lennaertmeijboom who put on @thevillagepitstop (where I did the first tattoos in the pics) and took such great care of us for the event. Feeling grateful and I love my friends
